      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HIGH GEAR MARIA (2) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from five starts. Below best last time at this track (22.41) in a Grade 5, finishing a 7 length sixth. Looks the one to beat with even luck. MENDOCINO (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (22.68) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Can measure up this time. BULLEMOR BANNER (8) isn't a quick beginner but comes home hard, finishing out of the frame two back but did wind up strongly to place when third (22.29) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including five wins. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from three starts. Expected to be in the finish again. RECKLESS RUBY (4) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
